SUMMARY:ARGENSIG - Argentina School on Internet Governance
DESCRIPTION:ARGENSIG is based in Argentina but welcomes fellows from across Latin Am
 erica\, both onsite and hybrid. Its central objective is to train future
  internet governance leaders\, covering the technical\, political\, econ
 omic\, social\, and legal dimensions of the digital ecosystem\, combinin
 g a global perspective with a focus on the specific challenges of Argent
 ina and the region.
URL:https://argensig.org/argensig2026/
