BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:3bab76af-ba73-57ff-bdbf-5ff074f83860
DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
SUMMARY:South School on Internet Governance (SSIG) Guatemala 2026
DESCRIPTION:The South School on Internet Governance (SSIG) Guatemala 2026 is a capac
 ity-building program designed to strengthen knowledge and skills on Inte
 rnet governance among participants from Guatemala and the Latin America 
 and Caribbean region. The program will address key topics such as Intern
 et governance processes\, multistakeholder participation\, cybersecurity
 \, Internet infrastructure\, digital policy\, and emerging technologies.
  This initiative promotes regional collaboration\, technical and policy 
 capacity development\, and active participation in national and internat
 ional Internet governance processes.
URL:https://gobernanzainternet.org/ssig2026/
DTSTART;TZID=CST:20260601T090000
DTEND;TZID=CST:20260605T170000
END:VEVENT
