DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
SUMMARY:Día Internacional de las Niñas en las TIC 2026 – Guatemala
DESCRIPTION:The International Girls in ICT Day 2026 in Guatemala aims to inspire and
  empower girls to explore careers in technology. The event will feature 
 keynote presentations\, interactive sessions\, and discussions on artifi
 cial intelligence\, digital skills\, and the role of girls in shaping th
 e digital future\, promoting STEM education and digital inclusion across
  Latin America and the Caribbean.
