DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
SUMMARY:Guatemala Internet Governance Forum 2026 (IGF Guatemala 2026)
DESCRIPTION:The Guatemala Internet Governance Forum (IGF Guatemala 2026) is a nation
 al multistakeholder platform bringing together government\, academia\, t
 he private sector\, civil society\, and the technical community to discu
 ss key internet governance issues. Topics include digital policy\, cyber
 security\, infrastructure\, connectivity\, artificial intelligence\, and
  emerging technologies. The forum promotes open dialogue and collaborati
 on to support a secure\, resilient\, and inclusive internet ecosystem in
  Guatemala and across Latin America and the Caribbean.
URL:https://igf.gt/2020/
DTSTART;TZID=CST:20261008T100000
DTEND;TZID=CST:20261008T160000
END:VEVENT
